\kappa(4,A)
A
A = \begin{bmatrix} 4 & 0 \\ 1000 & 2\end{bmatrix}
κ(λ, A) = \|y\|\|x\|
X_{\lambda}
X_{\lambda}^*
X_{\lambda}=A-\lambda I
X_{\lambda}x=0
y^*X_{\lambda}=0
 X_{4}=\begin{bmatrix}0 & 0 \\ 1000 & 2\end{bmatrix}. 
 x=\begin{bmatrix}-2/1000\\1\end{bmatrix},\quad y=\begin{bmatrix}1\\0\end{bmatrix} 
 \kappa_4\approx 500. 
